t still feels lost after reading it, this task is not done.","created_at":"2026-03-21T23:38:16Z"},{"id":352,"issue_id":"bd-j9jo3.6.1","author":"ubuntu","text":"Sensitivity follow-up: snapshot must surface disclosure-control markers and safe-preview semantics clearly enough that a first-contact agent understands when evidence is present but transformed, rather than mistaking redaction for missing data.","created_at":"2026-03-22T01:37:21Z"}]}
